For the first time since 1994, the Fed raises 75 BP.

Fed expects PCE inflation to be 5.2% in 2022 (previously 4.3%);

2.6% in 2023 and 2.2% in 2024. Medium Long-Term Forecast at 2.0% (previously 2.0%)
